<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>Ok, this is a great shield for a caster, noticing it has 15 AC. the con is it takes up the casters hand, and in later lvls, casters never ake hits, so this will really help at mid lvls, but at higher ones.... I would rather have and INT buffer or something.<BR>
<BR>
I got mine for 200, and love it.  If you can get a good deal on it, you should buy it. I'm a bard amd bought bladed thulian claws and this in one night. They combine perfectly. And at lvl 17 (duel weild) i can sell the shield for 350, getting 150 profit.<BR>
<BR>
And hey, this shield looks SWEET. </font></td></tr></table>
