<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white> I wanted to get one and tried to camp the place I was Mage 29-30 but it was really a delicate affair to clean the room. I recommend to use an Earth pet 29 to solo here and be ready to gate if one frog escapes or the train will kill you even if those are only greenies...One my first attempt i had to flee then came back later with a necro 29 to get to its spawn (on the left when you are facing the 3 shamans ). The Scryer only spawns once every 2 hours or roughly. Instead of its normal shaman placeholder you can find frog shin shaman 20th/ton knight 25th/ or gaz shaman and warriors in their 17th and even once a shin knight in its 27th who took me by surprised and nearly killed me. Once you have broken the spawn its fairly easy to hold it tho. I stayed for approx 7 to 8 hours and got on my 3 loots : grass woven/grass woven/shimmering orb. Guess i was luck. Theres also a no drop ench only mask for quest i believe. Beware tho, Scryer may charm you so its a good idea learning a cancel magic</font></td></tr></table>
